code: @Override protected TypeSerializer<?>[] getNestedSerializers(OptionSerializer<E> outerSerializer) {     return new TypeSerializer[] { outerSerializer.elemSerializer() }. }

@Override protected OptionSerializer<E> createOuterSerializerWithNestedSerializers(TypeSerializer<?>[] nestedSerializers) {     @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")     TypeSerializer<E> nestedSerializer = (TypeSerializer<E>) nestedSerializers[0].     return new OptionSerializer<>(nestedSerializer). }
